          <span class="sbp-accordion__caret"><svg width="12" height="8" viewBox="0 0 12 8" fill="none"><path d="M1 1L6 6L11 1" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg></span>
        </summary>
        <div class="sbp-accordion__body">
          <p class="sbp-accordion__ingredients">Yerba Mate · Darjeeling · Jiaogulan · Rooibos · Liu Bao · Long Jing · Oolong · Puerh</p>
          <p class="sbp-accordion__copy">Eight distinct teas from across the globe, each carrying its own unique profile of polyphenols, antioxidants, and natural compounds. Together they provide a gentle sustained release of natural energy without the cortisol-spiking effect of high-dose caffeine. Jiaogulan — known as Southern Ginseng — has been used in Chinese longevity traditions for centuries. Puerh is fermented and particularly valued for gut and metabolic support. Rooibos is naturally caffeine-free and rich in antioxidants.</p>
        </div>
      </details>

      <details class="sbp-accordion__item">
        <summary class="sbp-accordion__trigger">
          <span class="sbp-accordion__num">02</span>
          <span class="sbp-accordion__label">Algae &amp; Fungi Superfoods</span>
          <span class="sbp-accordion__caret"><svg width="12" height="8" viewBox="0 0 12 8" fill="none"><path d="M1 1L6 6L11 1" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg></span>
        </summary>
        <div class="sbp-accordion__body">
          <p class="sbp-accordion__ingredients">Marine Phytoplankton · Spirulina · Chlorella · Cordyceps · Lion's Mane · Reishi</p>
          <p class="sbp-accordion__copy">Marine phytoplankton is foundational cellular nutrition — a dense bioavailable source of micronutrients, amino acids, and essential fatty acids. Spirulina and chlorella deliver protein, vitamins, minerals, and support natural detoxification pathways. Cordyceps supports cellular energy and oxygen utilization. Lion's Mane is associated with supporting nerve growth factor and cognitive function. Reishi — the mushroom of immortality in Chinese medicine — is a powerful adaptogen that supports immune balance, stress resilience, and deep restoration.</p>
