      </details>

      <details class="sbp-accordion__item">
        <summary class="sbp-accordion__trigger">
          <span class="sbp-accordion__num">03</span>
          <span class="sbp-accordion__label">Spagyric Fermented Extracts</span>
          <span class="sbp-accordion__caret"><svg width="12" height="8" viewBox="0 0 12 8" fill="none"><path d="M1 1L6 6L11 1" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg></span>
        </summary>
        <div class="sbp-accordion__body">
          <p class="sbp-accordion__ingredients">Proprietary fermented spagyric botanical extracts</p>
          <p class="sbp-accordion__copy">This is the process that separates Wizard's Brew from everything else. Spagyric extraction uses ancient alchemical principles — fermentation, distillation, and purification — to produce whole-plant extracts of exceptional potency and bioavailability. The fermentation step also creates beneficial postbiotics, supporting the gut microbiome directly.</p>
