        </summary>
        <div class="sbp-faq__answer">
          <p>Yes — wholeheartedly. While the formulation is particularly supportive of women's hormonal health and longevity every ingredient supports the biology of all adults.</p>
        </div>
      </details>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

